Source: iubpatch
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Package Maintainer <advnpzn@proton.me>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13),
               cmake (>= 3.20),
               g++ (>= 10),
               pkg-config
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/advnpzn/IUBPatchLib
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: libiubpatch0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Library for IPS, UPS, and BPS binary patch formats
 IUBPatchLib is a modern, cross-platform C++ library for applying binary
 patches in IPS (International Patching System), UPS (Universal Patching
 System), and BPS (Binary Patching System) formats.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: libiubpatch-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libiubpatch0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for IUBPatchLib
 IUBPatchLib is a modern, cross-platform C++ library for applying binary
 patches in IPS, UPS, and BPS formats.
 .
 This package contains the development files (headers and pkg-config).

Package: iubpatch-tools
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Depends: libiubpatch0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command-line tools for IPS, UPS, and BPS patches
 Command-line utilities for applying and inspecting IPS, UPS, and BPS
 binary patches.
 .
 This package contains the iubpatch-cli tool.
